rbnCircuitGroupMib.name: rbnCircuitGroupMib

rbnCircuitGroupMib.description: Defines objects which may be used to monitor circuit groups policies

rbnCircuitGroupStatsTable.name: rbnCircuitGroupStatsTable
rbnCircuitGroupStatsTable.description: A table containing various Tx, Rx, and drop counters for each circuit group.

rbnCircuitGroupStatsEntry.name: rbnCircuitGroupStatsEntry
rbnCircuitGroupStatsEntry.description: A conceptual row in the rbnCircuitGroupStatsTable. Each row contains a set of packet and octet counters for a circuit group.

rbnCctGrpName.name: rbnCctGrpName
rbnCctGrpName.description: The name of the hierarchical group.

rbnCctGrpTxOctets.name: rbnCctGrpTxOctets
rbnCctGrpTxOctets.description: The number of octets transmitted by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpTxPackets.name: rbnCctGrpTxPackets
rbnCctGrpTxPackets.description: The number of packets transmitted by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpTxMulticastOctets.name: rbnCctGrpTxMulticastOctets
rbnCctGrpTxMulticastOctets.description: The number of multicast octets transmitted by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpTxMulticastPackets.name: rbnCctGrpTxMulticastPackets
rbnCctGrpTxMulticastPackets.description: The number of multicast packets transmitted by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpRxOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRxOctets
rbnCctGrpRxOctets.description: The number of octets received by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpRxPackets.name: rbnCctGrpRxPackets
rbnCctGrpRxPackets.description: The number of packets received by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpRxMulticastOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRxMulticastOctets
rbnCctGrpRxMulticastOctets.description: The number of multicast octets received by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpRxMulticastPackets.name: rbnCctGrpRxMulticastPackets
rbnCctGrpRxMulticastPackets.description: The number of multicast packets received by the group including its children.

rbnCctGrpAdjDroppedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpAdjDroppedOctets
rbnCctGrpAdjDroppedOctets.description: The number of adjacency octets dropped.

rbnCctGrpAdjDroppedPackets.name: rbnCctGrpAdjDroppedPackets
rbnCctGrpAdjDroppedPackets.description: The number of adjacency packets dropped.

rbnCctGrpDownDroppedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpDownDroppedOctets
rbnCctGrpDownDroppedOctets.description: The number of down octets dropped.

rbnCctGrpDownDroppedPackets.name: rbnCctGrpDownDroppedPackets
rbnCctGrpDownDroppedPackets.description: The number of down packets dropped.

rbnCctGrpUnreachDroppedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpUnreachDroppedOctets
rbnCctGrpUnreachDroppedOctets.description: The number of unreachable octets dropped.

rbnCctGrpUnreachDroppedPackets.name: rbnCctGrpUnreachDroppedPackets
rbnCctGrpUnreachDroppedPackets.description: The number of unreachable packets dropped.

rbnCctGrpUnknownEncapsOctets.name: rbnCctGrpUnknownEncapsOctets
rbnCctGrpUnknownEncapsOctets.description: The number octets dropped due to unknown encapsulation.

rbnCctGrpUnknownEncapsPackets.name: rbnCctGrpUnknownEncapsPackets
rbnCctGrpUnknownEncapsPackets.description: The number of packets dropped due to unknown encapsulation.

rbnCircuitGroupQTable.name: rbnCircuitGroupQTable
rbnCircuitGroupQTable.description: A table containing various counters for each transmit queue assigned to a circuit group.

rbnCircuitGroupQEntry.name: rbnCircuitGroupQEntry
rbnCircuitGroupQEntry.description: A conceptual row in the rbnCircuitGroupQueueTable. Each row contains tx and drop counters for each transmit queue assigned to a circuit group.

rbnCctGrpQueueId.name: rbnCctGrpQueueId
rbnCctGrpQueueId.description: A unique identifier for a transmit queue used by the circuit.

rbnCctGrpQTxOctets.name: rbnCctGrpQTxOctets
rbnCctGrpQTxOctets.description: The number of octets transmitted out of this queue. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system.

rbnCctGrpQTxPackets.name: rbnCctGrpQTxPackets
rbnCctGrpQTxPackets.description: The number of packets transmitted out of this queue. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system.

rbnCctGrpQWredDroppedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpQWredDroppedOctets
rbnCctGrpQWredDroppedOctets.description: The number of octets dropped due to the application of a weighted random early detection algorithm. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system.

rbnCctGrpQWredDroppedPkts.name: rbnCctGrpQWredDroppedPkts
rbnCctGrpQWredDroppedPkts.description: The number of packets dropped due to the application of a weighted random early detection algorithm. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system.

rbnCctGrpQTailDroppedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpQTailDroppedOctets
rbnCctGrpQTailDroppedOctets.description: The number of octets dropped when the total number of packets in this queue was greater than the maximum threshold. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system.

rbnCctGrpQTailDroppedPkts.name: rbnCctGrpQTailDroppedPkts
rbnCctGrpQTailDroppedPkts.description: The number of packets dropped when the total number of packets in this queue was greater than the maximum threshold. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyStatsTable.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyStatsTable
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyStatsTable.description: A table of counters for rate limit policies applied to circuit groups.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyStatsEntry.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyStatsEntry
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyStatsEntry.description: A conceptial row in the rbnCircuitGroupPolicyStatsTable. Each row contains counters for a rate limit policy applied to the circuit group. Note that each counter includes the sum of all the child circuits.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyType.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyType
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyType.description: The type of the rate-limit policy which is applied to the circuit group.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyConformOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyConformOctets
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyConformOctets.description: The number of octets that conform to the rate limit set on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyConformPkts.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyConformPkts
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyConformPkts.description: The number of packets that conform to the rate limit set on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedOctets
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedOctets.description: The number of octets that exceed the rate limit set on the interface for which class counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedPkts.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedPkts
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedPkts.description: The number of packets that exceed the rate limit set on the interface.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedDroppedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedDroppedOctets
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedDroppedOctets.description: The number of octets that were dropped due to the application of an exceed action on packets that exceed the rate limit set on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedDroppedPkts.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedDroppedPkts
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyExceedDroppedPkts.description: The number of packets that were dropped due to the application of an exceed action on packets that exceed the rate limit set on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateOctets
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateOctets.description: The number of octets that violate the normal and maximum burst sizes on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolatePkts.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolatePkts
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolatePkts.description: The number of packets that violate the normal and maximum burst sizes on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateDroppedOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateDroppedOctets
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateDroppedOctets.description: The number of octets that were dropped due to the application of a violate action on packets that violate the normal and maximum burst sizes on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateDroppedPkts.name: rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateDroppedPkts
rbnCctGrpRLPolicyViolateDroppedPkts.description: The number of packets that were dropped due to the application of a violate action on packets that violate the normal and maximum burst sizes on the circuit group for which counters are enabled.

rbnCctGrpRLClassStatsTable.name: rbnCctGrpRLClassStatsTable
rbnCctGrpRLClassStatsTable.description: A table of counters for rate limit policy classes applied to circuit groups.

rbnCctGrpRLClassStatsEntry.name: rbnCctGrpRLClassStatsEntry
rbnCctGrpRLClassStatsEntry.description: A conceptial row in the rbnCctGrpRLClassStatsTable. Each row contains counters for a rate limit policy class applied to the circuit group.

rbnCctGrpRLClassId.name: rbnCctGrpRLClassId
rbnCctGrpRLClassId.description: A value that uniquely identifies a class defined in the rate-limit policy access list.

rbnCctGrpRLClassName.name: rbnCctGrpRLClassName
rbnCctGrpRLClassName.description: Name of the class in the rate-limit policy access list.

rbnCctGrpRLClassConformOctets.name: rbnCctGrpRLClassConformOctets
rbnCctGrpRLClassConformOctets.description: The number of octets that conform to the policy class rate limit set on the circuit group.

rbnCctGrpRLClassConformPkts.description: The number of packets that conform to the policy class rate limit set on the circuit group.

rbnCctGrpRLClassConformDroppedPkts.description: The number of packets that were dropped due to the application of a conform action on packets that conform to the policy class rate limit set on the circuit group.
